WEBVTT

00:00:10.489 --> 00:00:18.706 line:90% position:50% align:center
Earth cries out ev’ry day.
So many have lost their way.

00:00:19.582 --> 00:00:29.466 line:90% position:50% align:center
Wars never cease; fighting for peace,
Man cannot find the answers.

00:00:29.466 --> 00:00:37.683 line:90% position:50% align:center
Through all these stormy seas
And empty philosophies,

00:00:38.434 --> 00:00:47.568 line:90% position:50% align:center
Jehovah provides a hope for mankind,
A world we’re longing to see:

00:00:48.360 --> 00:00:58.621 line:90% position:50% align:center
One faith, one God,
Peace on earth,

00:00:58.621 --> 00:01:09.173 line:90% position:50% align:center
One mind, one voice
Throughout the universe

00:01:11.759 --> 00:01:19.308 line:90% position:50% align:center
When all hearts sing as one.

00:01:25.731 --> 00:01:34.448 line:90% position:50% align:center
Know that this hope is sure
Despite what we might endure.

00:01:34.448 --> 00:01:44.249 line:90% position:50% align:center
Jehovah is there and lovingly shares
Peace that flows like a river,

00:01:44.249 --> 00:01:53.133 line:90% position:50% align:center
Calming our doubts and fears,
Drying up ev’ry tear.

00:01:53.133 --> 00:02:03.435 line:90% position:50% align:center
Forever we’ll find true peace of mind,
Knowing soon we will see:

00:02:03.435 --> 00:02:14.029 line:90% position:50% align:center
One faith, one God,
Peace on earth,

00:02:14.029 --> 00:02:25.582 line:90% position:50% align:center
One mind, one voice
Throughout the universe

00:02:26.875 --> 00:02:35.134 line:90% position:50% align:center
When all hearts sing as one.

00:02:36.510 --> 00:02:45.185 line:90% position:50% align:center
Under the Prince of Peace,
Freedom will never end.

00:02:45.185 --> 00:02:50.566 line:90% position:50% align:center
When sorrow is gone
and death is undone,

00:02:50.566 --> 00:03:00.909 line:90% position:50% align:center
Every knee will bend
To Jehovah, our King.

00:03:02.536 --> 00:03:13.088 line:90% position:50% align:center
One faith, one God,
Peace on earth,

00:03:13.088 --> 00:03:24.725 line:90% position:50% align:center
One mind, one voice
Throughout the universe—

